ce memories of this position - see the game Aabling- Schandorff (See "Aabling- Schandorff" variation from the PGN), Denmark 2010 in the Model Games. } * 

[Event "A Deep Dive into the Caro-Kann: Advance Variation for Black"]
[Site "4.Nc3 Shirov: 7.h4 with 9.Nxh5 #3"]
[Date "????.??.??"]
