lack is doing fine after the following continuation. } 15... Qd6 { Covering the bishop. } 16. Bh5+ Bg6 { [%csl Rh2] Black is fine. White has compensation, but nothing more than that. Two sample lines go: • • Or } 17. Bg4 ( 17. c5 Qd7 18. Nxe6 $1 Qxe6 19. Re1 Qf7 $1 20. Rxe5 Bxh5 21. Qxh5 Qxh5 22. Rxh5 O-O { with a balanced ending. } ) 17... h5 18. c5 $1 $2 Bxh2+ 19. Kh1 hxg4 $1 20. cxd6 Bxd6+ 21. Kg1 Bh2+ 22. Kh1 Bg3+ { with a draw by repetition. } * 

