tinued } 17. b4 O-O 18. b5 Qa5 19. cxd5 exd5 20. Qd3 { and here Caruana took on h4. Stronger was } 20... Qc7 $1 { , threatening mate. After } 21. g3 g6 22. Rfe1 Rfe8 { Black is certainly not worse. } * 

